Game.Name: J. League Greatest Eleven (Japan)
Game.plot: Overview:J-League Greatest Eleven features the Japanese soccer league's ten teams from its inaugural 1993 season. There's an exhibition mode with support for four players and a league mode where 1 or 2 players can face off against the computer.
